title: can't queue up in games
body: when i go into lobby and try click the "find match" button, nothing happens but the button remains clickable. I've been waiting for 2 hours and nothing is still happening. is anyone else facing this issue? What is the solution? I've been clicking the "find match" button for ages but i don't go into queue and the button remains clickable

replies.body: if you try and start a custon game, it will tell you that you are "in-game" which means that the client is telling itself you are still loaded into the game you started, same thing is happening to me.

yea seems like alot of people going through this right now i was ion champ select like 3 hours ago now and still cant Que up we all had to leave and re log now no one can Que i can Que up on my alt but not my main that i was in the champ select
